                <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܛܟܣܐ ܕܐܪ̈ܒܥܝܢ ܣܗ̈ܕܐ ܩ̈ܕܝܫܐ</rubric>
                
                
                
                
                
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="b19" n="22">
                <locus to="211" from="206a">Foll. 206a-211</locus>
                
                <title xml:lang="en">Of the holy Prophets, especially of
                              <persName>Elias</persName>.</title>
                <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܛܟܣܐ ܕܥܠ ܢܒ̈ܝܐ ܩ̈ܕܝܫܐ ܘܥܠ ܐܠܝܐ ܢܒܝܐ</rubric>
                
                
                
                
                <note>The above services comprise hymns of several kinds (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܥ̈ܢܝܢܐ,
