                           <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/13">Ephraim</persName>.</note>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="b20" n="23">
                <locus to="213" from="211b">Foll. 211b-213</locus>
                
                <title xml:lang="en">Hymns to be chanted at mealtimes.</title>
                <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܛܟ̣ܣܐ ܕܩ̈ܠܐ ܕܥܠ ܦܬܘܪܐ</rubric>
                
                
                
                
                
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="b21" n="24">
                <locus to="213" from="213b">Foll. 213b-213</locus>
                
                <title xml:lang="en">Anthems to be used on assuming the monastic
